Introduction

Ji Suyeon is a South Korean singer, producer, musical actress, TV personality, and radio host under Bomnal Entertainment. She is best known as the leader and main vocalist of Weki Meki.

Before debuting with the group in 2017, she trained under CJ E&M and WM Entertainment and appeared on the Chinese survival show 'Ladybees'. Later in her career she made her musical theatre debut with the musical 'Bungee Jumping of Their Own' in 2022.

As a producer and lyricist, she has contributed to Weki Meki's music and produced NiziU's "Press Play". In 2025, she signed with Bomnal Entertainment to continue her career in music and theater.
